videos.description: Steven Sims Jr. tries to field a punt but fumbles the ball and turns it over to Iowa State.
videos.headline: Jayhawks make a costly mistake

videos.description: Jayhawks' QB Payton Bender throws a pass deep down the field and it bounces off his receivers hands into Cyclones' CB Kamari Cotton-Moya's hands who returns it 23 yards.
videos.headline: Iowa State defense gets an unusual turnover

videos.description: WR Deshaunte Jones gets open on the bubble screen and breaks a few tackles to pick up the first down.
videos.headline: Cyclones showing some toughness

videos.description: Iowa State's Trever Ryen gets a couple of huge blocks and returns the punt 68 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Cyclones' big blocks lead to punt return TD

videos.description: RB David Montgomery takes the handoff and lowers his helmet to score a 4-yard touchdown after a Kansas turnover.
videos.headline: Iowa State takes advantage of Kansas miscue

videos.description: David Montgomery goes over the top of the defense for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Montgomery gets his second TD of the day

videos.description: Kansas punter Cole Moos mishandles the high snap and falls on the ball.
videos.headline: Jayhawks woes on special teams continue

videos.description: Cole Moos botches a snap for the second time in the game and gets off a terrible kick.
videos.headline: Kansas having nightmares on special teams

videos.description: Kyle Kempt finds WR Marchi Murdock on a short pass and he jukes a defender to score an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa State offense pouring it on

videos.description: Backup QB Zeb Noland throws a 24-yard laser to TE Jalen Martin who makes a leaping catch for the first down.
videos.headline: Cyclones' TE Martin makes a nice grab

videos.description: RB Sheldon Croney Jr. cuts to the right and runs it in for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa State showing no mercy
